OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FLonger lorries to be       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fallowed on Britain's roads 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government has approved the use of 
OL,6, longer lorries on British roads, saying
OL,7, it will make businesses more efficient 
OL,8, and cut emissions.                     
OL,10,FIt comes despite one campaign group    
OL,11,Fwarning the move could put pedestrians 
OL,12,Fand cyclists at risk.                  
OL,14,FLonger lorries can carry more goods in 
OL,15,Ffewer trips but have a larger tail     
OL,16,Fswing, meaning their rear end covers a 
OL,17,Fgreater area when turning. They also   
OL,18,Fhave extended blind spots.             
OL,20,FBut ministers insist they are safe.    
